---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import LegalPage from '../../components/LegalPage.astro';
import { site } from '../../data/site.js';
---

<MainLayout
  lang="en"
  title="Privacy policy"
  description="Privacy policy of Zurano y Blázquez. Information on how we process personal data collected through zuranoyblazquez.com."
  noindex={true}
>
  <LegalPage title="Privacy policy">
    <p class="notice">
      Provisional text pending legal review. This policy must be reviewed by legal counsel before
      final publication.
    </p>

    <h2>1. Data controller</h2>
    <p>
      The controller of personal data collected through this website is {site.legalName}, contact
      email <a href={`mailto:${site.email}`}>{site.email}</a>.
    </p>

    <h2>2. Purpose of processing</h2>
    <p>
      Personal data submitted through the contact form will be used solely to respond to information
      requests and to manage the commercial relationship arising from such requests.
    </p>

    <h2>3. Legal basis</h2>
    <p>
      Processing is based on the consent of the data subject when submitting the contact form, and on
      the legitimate interest in managing enquiries received.
    </p>

    <h2>4. Data retention</h2>
    <p>
      Data will be retained for as long as necessary to respond to the enquiry and, where applicable,
      for the periods required by applicable law.
    </p>

    <h2>5. Rights of data subjects</h2>
    <p>
      You may exercise your rights of access, rectification, erasure, restriction, objection and
      portability by writing to <a href={`mailto:${site.email}`}>{site.email}</a>. You also have the
      right to lodge a complaint with the relevant supervisory authority.
    </p>

    <h2>6. Security</h2>
    <p>
      {site.legalName} applies appropriate technical and organisational measures to protect personal
      data against unauthorised access, alteration or disclosure.
    </p>
  </LegalPage>
</MainLayout>
